text: Sud-Vest (South West) or Sud-Vest Oltenia is a development region in Romania. It almost the same area as the historic region of Oltenia. It is called sometimes Regiunea de dezvoltare Sud-Vest Oltenia. County population 2011 Dolj 630,124 Gorj 345,771 Mehedinți 259,212 Olt 421,769 Vâlcea 374,240 Total 2,031,116 Source: == References == * Description of the region South-West Category:Development regions of Romania
